The user was then posed two questions regarding the positioning and color of the button, with options for the top or bottom of the screen, and blue or green coloring. Furthermore, the user requested a second button labeled "Hello World," to which the AI similarly responded affirmatively. It presented another list of additional features for this button, including a floating action button for alerts, a search bar for news, notification bell, and a dropdown menu for categories. The user was again asked two questions to decide the position and color of the "Hello World" button, with different options. The AI acknowledged both requests effectively during the conversation.
